This article presents the '''discography''' of [[United States|American]] [[pop music]] singer, '''[[Michael Bolton]]'''. Since 1976, Bolton has released 17 studio albums and 35 singles. Nine of Bolton' [[single (music)|singles]] have peaked at #1 on either the [[Billboard Hot 100]] or the [[Hot Adult Contemporary Tracks]] charts in the United States.

